A 3-in-1 product, this scrub exfoliates, cleanses and moisturizes theskin. The sugar hydrates and gently polishes off impurities to promote aglowing complexion, while the blend of Rose Geranium and Rosemary essentialoils create a herbaceous scent that is wonderful for encouraging healthycognitive functions as well as tranquility.

Key Ingredients:

-Sucrose:

Sucrose acts as a natural humectant, good for preserving moisture. Asan exfoliant, it is very delicate and can be used even on sensitive skins topolish away dead skin cells while ensuring dewiness and elasticity. Results arenoticeably smooth and radiant after a few use.

-Rad’sBotanic Emollient Blend:

Cocoa and Shea Butter - ingredients known to be used in ancient beautyrituals - are carefully sourced for this scrub to create a rich hydratingexperience for your skin. Packed with fatty acids and polyphenols, our softbotanical butter helps reduce the appearance of scars while preserving theskin’s natural moisture barrier. Coconut and Sweet Almond oils add arevitalizing boost of Vitamin E, a wonderful aid for maintaining healthy skin.  

Directions:

Scoop with the spatula provided,gently massage into damp skin with circular motion until the sugar dissolve.Give extra attention to rough area. Rinse off.

Cautions:

Testpatch prior usage.

Donot use on a sunburn, after shaving or other skin condition. 

Packaging:

Packaged in 220gm reusable jar. Gives approximately 6-8scrub experiences.

Keep unused portion dry. Avoid direct sunlight. Discardafter 6 months of opening.

Full Ingredients:

Sucrose (Fine Sugar), Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil,Prunus Amygdalus (Sweet Almond) Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea Butter), Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa Butter), Cetearyl Olivate , Sorbitan Olivate,Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, PelargoniumGraveolens (Rose Geranium) Oil, Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary) Oil.

A 3-in-1 product, this scrub exfoliates, cleanses and moisturizes the skin. Enriched with hydratingbotanical ingredients such as shea butter and sweet almond oil, this sugar scrub gentlyexfoliates and nourishes dull skin to reveal a soft, supple and smoothcomplexion. Specially blended with Lavender and Bergamot essential oils to easestress and help you relax.

Key Ingredients:

Sucrose:

Sucrose acts as a natural humectant, good for preserving moisture. Asan exfoliant, it is very delicate and can be used even on sensitive skins topolish away dead skin cells while ensuring dewiness and elasticity. Results arenoticeably smooth and radiant after a few use.

Rad’sBotanic Emollient Blend:

Cocoa and Shea Butter - ingredients known to be used in ancient beautyrituals - are carefully sourced for this scrub to create a rich hydratingexperience for your skin. Packed with fatty acids and polyphenols, our softbotanical butter helps reduce the appearance of scars while preserving theskin’s natural moisture barrier. Coconut and Sweet Almond oils add arevitalizing boost of Vitamin E, a wonderful aid for maintaining healthy skin. 

Directions:

Scoop with the spatula provided, gently massage intodamp skin with circular motion until the sugar dissolve. Give extra attentionto rough area. Rinse off.

Cautions:

Testpatch prior usage.

Donot use on a sunburn, after shaving or other skin condition. 

Packaging:

Packaged in 220gm reusable jar. Gives approximately 6-8scrub experiences.

A 3-in-1 product, this scrub exfoliates, cleanses and moisturizes the skin. This luscious sugar scrub gently eliminates dead skin cells whilereplenishing moisture for a smooth and radiant complexion. When used after along day, this piquant scrub with its bursts of citrus aroma, help reducestress and promote an uplifting mood.

Key Ingredients:

Sucrose:

Sucrose acts as a natural humectant, good for preserving moisture. Asan exfoliant, it is very delicate and can be used even on sensitive skins topolish away dead skin cells while ensuring dewiness and elasticity. Results arenoticeably smooth and radiant after a few use.

Rad’sBotanic Emollient Blend:

Cocoa and Shea Butter - ingredients known to be used in ancient beautyrituals - are carefully sourced for this scrub to create a rich hydratingexperience for your skin. Packed with fatty acids and polyphenols, our softbotanical butter helps reduce the appearance of scars while preserving theskin’s natural moisture barrier. Coconut and Sweet Almond oils add arevitalizing boost of Vitamin E, a wonderful aid for maintaining healthyskin. 

Directions:

Scoop with the spatula provided, gently massage intodamp skin with circular motion until the sugar dissolve. Give extra attentionto rough area. Rinse off.

Cautions:

Testpatch prior usage.

Donot use on a sunburn, after shaving or other skin condition.  

Packaging:

Packaged in 220gm reusable jar. Gives approximately 6-8scrub experiences.

Keep unused portion dry. Avoid direct sunlight. Discardafter 6 months of opening.

Full Ingredients:

Sucrose (Fine Sugar), Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil,Prunus Amygdalus (Sweet Almond) Oil, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea Butter), Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa Butter), Cetearyl Olivate , Sorbitan Olivate,Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycerin, Citrus Limonum (Lemon) Oil, CitrusParadisi (Grapefruit) Oil & Citrus Sinesis (Sweet Orange) Oil.

Caution: Photo toxic. Lemon essential oil maycause skin irritation.

-Provides delicate, defining finish with flat shaped stick which prevents colors from feathering or bleeding

Silky Texture System

-‘Silicon cross polymer’ that feels weightless & non-sticky, makes the texture glide over by filling up the fine lines of the lips.

-‘Oil gel’ creates silky smooth, wrinkle-free lips.

-Enabling matt, powdery finish

 

High Glossy Polymer Network

-A ‘Polymer network’ is built when the formula is applied on the skin. It helps pigments to fit onto the lips and coats the surface evenly. Eventually this results in a ultra-glossy shine and intense color expression.

-Enabling moisturizing finish, excellent gloss without stickiness

Ingredients:

Moisturization

Argan Oil

-     Argan oil has nourishing and hydrating effects which keeps the skin highly moisturized. Argan oil is derived from the Argan Trees in the Moroccan desert. It contains twice more Vitamin E than olive oil, which acts to protect skin from loss of moisture.

Rosehip Oil

-    Rosehip oil contains Pro-vitamin A (mostly Beta-carotene), and Retinoicacid. It is also rich in Essential fatty acids such as Omega-6 and Omega-3. Rosehip oil is quickly absorbed into the skin and it hydrates the skin by creating a protective layer. It is well known for the key benefit that keeping skin texture smooth and soft, it is generally used as base material of various cosmetic products. Also, it is known to help to relieve skin inflammation, cure acne, eczema, sunburn, and care for extremely dry skin.

Trouble relief

Calendula Oil

-    Derived from marigold flowers, calendula oil has medicinal benefits for atopic skin. As a remedy to treat atopic skin disease, it is widely used as a base material of soap, facial cream, and many other cosmetic products. Calendula oil is effective in curing eczema, skin inflammation, and wounds.

Jojoba Oil

-    Jojoba oil helps to keep the skin moisturized and treats skin inflammation. It is a toxic-free, rich in vitamins & minerals which act for skin protection, alleviation of skin trouble and skin moisturization.

Olive Oil

-    With its concentration of squalene, plant sterols, tocopherol and polyphenol, olive oil acts as an excellent antioxidant in human body. It also has deintoxication effect, boosts the immune system, controls hormones and works as antibiotics.

A flat stick type lip product for vivid color expression as well as velvety / glossy finish in just one stroke

Size : 1.8g

-Provides delicate, defining finish with flat shaped stick which prevents colors from feathering or bleeding

-Captivating color expression & high-impact finish, only with a single touch

-Highly pigmented formula delivers brilliant look of color

Silky Texture System

-‘Silicon cross polymer’ that feels weightless & non-sticky, makes the texture glide over by filling up the fine lines of the lips.

-‘Oil gel’ creates silky smooth, wrinkle-free lips.

-Enabling matt, powdery finish

 

High Glossy Polymer Network

-A ‘Polymer network’ is built when the formula is applied on the skin. It helps pigments to fit onto the lips and coats the surface evenly. Eventually this results in a ultra-glossy shine and intense color expression.

-Enabling moisturizing finish, excellent gloss without stickiness

Ingredients:

Moisturization

Argan Oil

-     Argan oil has nourishing and hydrating effects which keeps the skin highly moisturized. Argan oil is derived from the Argan Trees in the Moroccan desert. It contains twice more Vitamin E than olive oil, which acts to protect skin from loss of moisture.

Rosehip Oil

-    Rosehip oil contains Pro-vitamin A (mostly Beta-carotene), and Retinoicacid. It is also rich in Essential fatty acids such as Omega-6 and Omega-3. Rosehip oil is quickly absorbed into the skin and it hydrates the skin by creating a protective layer. It is well known for the key benefit that keeping skin texture smooth and soft, it is generally used as base material of various cosmetic products. Also, it is known to help to relieve skin inflammation, cure acne, eczema, sunburn, and care for extremely dry skin.

Trouble relief

Calendula Oil

-    Derived from marigold flowers, calendula oil has medicinal benefits for atopic skin. As a remedy to treat atopic skin disease, it is widely used as a base material of soap, facial cream, and many other cosmetic products. Calendula oil is effective in curing eczema, skin inflammation, and wounds.

Jojoba Oil

-    Jojoba oil helps to keep the skin moisturized and treats skin inflammation. It is a toxic-free, rich in vitamins & minerals which act for skin protection, alleviation of skin trouble and skin moisturization.

Olive Oil

-    With its concentration of squalene, plant sterols, tocopherol and polyphenol, olive oil acts as an excellent antioxidant in human body. It also has deintoxication effect, boosts the immune system, controls hormones and works as antibiotics.
